Eastern Ave. , Las Vegas, NV, 89123', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 5', 'OR Text', '5', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Welcome To Rancho Serene', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1205 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Rancho Serene, a community of luxury apartment homes with features and amenities that will impress you at a price that will surprise you.', 'Rancho Serene is conveniently located just west of Green Valley, immediately off I-215 in Las Vegas, Nevada which makes it perfect for getting to work.', 'Rancho brings fabulous shopping, entertainment, restaurants and schools to your doorstep.', 'Our community combines the convenience of a metropolitan city with the ease of a resort experience.', "Call Now to speak with a leasing specialist about the apartment home that's right for you!", 'Features', '- Washer and Dryer', '- Roman Tubs', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '- Spacious Walk-In Closets', '- Central Air and Heat', '- Cable Ready', '- Extra Storage', '- Private Balcony or Patio', '- Gas Fireplace*', '- Disposal', '- Microwave', '- Refrigerator', '- Dishwasher', '*Available in Select Units', 'Community Amenities', '- Onsite and On Call Maintenance', '- Sundeck', '- Swimming Pool & Spa', '- Media Room', '- Garages', '- Fully Equipped Fitness Center', '- Gated Access', '- Spanish Speaking Staff', '-', '- Elegant Clubhouse', '- Availability 24 Hours', '- On-Site Management', '- High Speed Internet', '- Easy Access to Freeways and Shopping', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- Package Receiving', '- Covered Parking', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday 8:00 AM-5:00 PM', 'Saturday 8:00 AM-5:00 PM', 'Sunday 10:00 AM-4:00 PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed, Max weight 35 lb each, One time Fee $200.00 (1 pet), $250 (2 pets), Rent $30.00, Deposit $100.00', 'Restrictions: Pets Upon Approval', '180navcxMa']
